Package: GSEexplore
Title: Interactive Exploration of Gene Expression Omnibus Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "GSEexplore",
           family = "Contributors",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "info@gseexplore.dev")
Description: A Shiny application for interactive exploration of GEO (Gene Expression Omnibus) datasets.
    Fetch expression data by GSE accession, perform quality control assessments, and run differential
    expression analysis using limma. Includes visualization of PCA, sample distributions, and DE results.
